  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `PlaybookOutputHandler.cs` switch.</step>
    <step order="2">Add `FormPrefill` case with explicit `return Task.CompletedTask;` (or method-shape equivalent). Add a code comment citing NFR-07 + spec FR-14d.</step>
    <step order="3">Add unit test: invoke handler with `NodeDestination = FormPrefill`; assert no SSE event captured + no chat token emitted.</step>
    <step order="4">Regression test (existing): `useAiPrefill` end-to-end pre-fill flow still works (no change to that flow expected; this test confirms).</step>
    <step order="5">Run `dotnet build` + tests; measure publish delta.</step>
    <step order="6">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 050 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

